<br>
EQ marriages/affairs...are just that...&quot;EQ marriages/affairs&quot;...why does it have to be taken into the RL world .....as long as the 2 people never actually met in RL?<br>
<br>
Why would someone's spouse even care about online affairs if they never met in the first place? Online affairs is just that...online and part of F-A-N-T-A-S-Y. I just dont get why spouses even give a crap about anything that happens online.<br>
<br>
If it had resulted in an actualy meeting and RL encounter/affair...THEN the spouse has a right to be pissed/upset/feel betrayed. Come on...how many times have any of you &quot;fantasized&quot; about being with another person other than your spouse when you are having sex?<br>
<br>
